<br>
thing is, it has to be rootable...and root has to stick well.<br>
<br>
basically, the tactic is to root/dot as hard as you can, while backing out when summoned, and healing yourself as necessary.  Thorns and all the regen you can muster helps.<br>
<br>
It's hard, and there's a limit to how tough a mob you can do, but it's definitely doable.  Expect to die a lot until you get the hang of it.<br>
